  <ul>
  <li>A number specifies the number of <strong>hours</strong> before a duplicate alert will be sent to the email address(es) specified in the <strong>Who</strong> field.</li>
  <li>An empty field causes those messages to be <strong>ignored.</strong></li>
  <li>A value of 0 (zero) causes <strong>every</strong> alert (duplicate or not) to be sent.</li>
  </ul>
